{"name":"ritemark","displayName": "Ritemark Editor","description":"WYSIWYG Markdown Editor","version": "1.1.1","publisher":"ritemark","license":"MIT","engines":{"vscode":"^1.94.0"},"main":"./out/extension.js","activationEvents":["onCustomEditor:ritemark.editor","onCustomEditor:ritemark.excelViewer","onView:ritemark.unifiedView","onCommand:ritemark.configureApiKey","onCommand:ritemark.showAIPanel","onCommand:ritemark.openSearch"],"contributes":{"commands":[{"command":"ritemark.configureApiKey","title":"Ritemark: Configure OpenAI API Key"},{"command":"ritemark.showAIPanel","title":"Ritemark: Show AI Assistant","icon":"$(sparkle)"},{"command":"ritemark.openSearch","title":"Search","icon":"$(search)"},{"command":"ritemark.reindexDocuments","title":"Ritemark: Re-index Documents"},{"command":"ritemark.newChat","title":"New Chat","icon":"$(add)"},{"command":"ritemark.aiSettings","title":"AI Settings","icon":"$(gear)"},{"command":"ritemark.flows.new","title":"New Flow","icon":"$(add)"},{"command":"ritemark.flows.refresh","title":"Refresh Flows","icon":"$(refresh)"}],"configuration":[{"title":"Ritemark Updates","properties":{"ritemark.updates.enabled":{"type":"boolean","default":true,"description":"Check for updates on startup"},"ritemark.updates.dismissed":{"type":"string","default":"","description":"Last dismissed update version (internal)"}}},{"title":"Ritemark Features","properties":{"ritemark.features.voice-dictation":{"type":"boolean","default":false,"description":"Enable voice dictation (experimental, macOS only). Requires Whisper model download (~75MB).","scope":"application"},"ritemark.features.ritemark-flows":{"type":"boolean","default":false,"description":"Enable RiteMark Flows (experimental) - Visual automation workflows with AI and file operations.","scope":"application"}}}],"viewsContainers":{"activitybar":[{"id":"ritemark-ai","title":"Ritemark AI","icon":"media/bot-icon.svg"}]},"views":{"ritemark-ai":[{"type":"webview","id":"ritemark.unifiedView","name":"Ritemark AI","contextualTitle":"Ritemark AI","visibility":"collapsed"},{"type":"webview","id":"ritemark.flowsView","name":"Flows","contextualTitle":"Flows","when":"config.ritemark.features.ritemark-flows"}]},"menus":{"editor/title":[{"command":"ritemark.showAIPanel","group":"navigation","when":"activeCustomEditorId == ritemark.editor"}],"view/title":[{"command":"ritemark.openSearch","when":"view == workbench.explorer.fileView","group":"navigation@1"},{"command":"ritemark.newChat","when":"view == ritemark.unifiedView","group":"navigation@1"},{"command":"ritemark.aiSettings","when":"view == ritemark.unifiedView","group":"navigation@2"},{"command":"ritemark.flows.new","when":"view == ritemark.flowsView","group":"navigation@1"},{"command":"ritemark.flows.refresh","when":"view == ritemark.flowsView","group":"navigation@2"}]},"customEditors":[{"viewType":"ritemark.editor","displayName":"Ritemark","selector":[{"filenamePattern":"*.md"},{"filenamePattern":"*.markdown"},{"filenamePattern":"*.csv"}],"priority":"exclusive"},{"viewType":"ritemark.excelViewer","displayName":"Excel Preview","selector":[{"filenamePattern":"*.xlsx"},{"filenamePattern":"*.xls"}],"priority":"exclusive"}],"configurationDefaults":{"files.autoSave":"afterDelay","files.autoSaveDelay":1000,"workbench.sideBar.location":"left","workbench.colorTheme":"Default Light Modern","workbench.iconTheme":"ritemark-icons","workbench.activityBar.location":"default","extensions.ignoreRecommendations":true,"workbench.tips.enabled":false,"debug.showInStatusBar":"never","testing.openTesting":"neverOpen","outline.showVariables":false,"outline.showFunctions":false,"timeline.showUncommittedChanges":false,"window.autoDetectColorScheme":false,"workbench.preferredLightColorTheme":"Default Light Modern","workbench.preferredDarkColorTheme":"Default Light Modern","chat.commandCenter.enabled":false,"chat.agent.enabled":false,"github.copilot.enable":{"*":false},"github.copilot.editor.enableAutoCompletions":false,"github.copilot.editor.enableCodeActions":false,"workbench.panel.defaultLocation":"right"},"walkthroughs":[{"id":"ritemark.welcome","title":"Get Started with Ritemark","description":"A beautiful markdown editor with AI assistance","steps":[{"id":"welcome","title":"Welcome to Ritemark","description":"Write in markdown with a clean, distraction-free interface. Your files stay on your computer.","media":{"svg":"media/logo.svg"},"completionEvents":["onStepSelected"]},{"id":"configureApiKey","title":"Configure AI API Key","description":"Optional: Add your OpenAI API key to enable AI writing assistance.\n\n[Configure API Key](command:ritemark.configureApiKey)","completionEvents":["onCommand:ritemark.configureApiKey"]},{"id":"openMarkdown","title":"Open a Markdown File","description":"Open any `.md` file to start writing.\n\n[Open File](command:workbench.action.files.openFileFolder)","completionEvents":["onCommand:workbench.action.files.openFileFolder"]},{"id":"tryAI","title":"Try AI Features","description":"Select text and use the AI panel to rephrase, expand, or improve your writing.\n\n[Show AI Panel](command:ritemark.showAIPanel)","completionEvents":["onCommand:ritemark.showAIPanel"]}]}],"iconThemes":[{"id":"ritemark-icons","label":"Ritemark Icons","path":"./fileicons/ritemark-icon-theme.json"}]},"scripts":{"compile":"tsc -p ./","watch":"tsc -watch -p ./","test":"npx tsx src/features/featureGate.test.ts"},"dependencies":{"@tanstack/react-table":"^8.21.3","@tanstack/react-virtual":"^3.13.18","@types/marked":"^5.0.2","@types/pdfkit":"^0.17.4","@orama/orama":"^3.1.0","docx":"^8.5.0","gray-matter":"^4.0.3","marked":"^4.3.0","openai":"^4.73.0","papaparse":"^5.5.3","pdfkit":"^0.17.2","turndown":"^7.2.0","turndown-plugin-gfm":"^1.0.2","xlsx":"^0.18.5"},"devDependencies":{"@types/node":"^24.10.8","@types/papaparse":"^5.5.2","@types/turndown":"^5.0.5","@types/vscode":"^1.94.0","lucide-static":"^0.555.0","typescript":"^5.0.0"}}